text:
Teachers at O'Leary Middle School were missing interactions with their students. They felt like they hadn't been able to give students the usual amount of encouragement so they shared hundreds of uplifting messages with their students on the YouUplift platform. #MissYouMonday You can see the messages here:

https://youuplift.com/oleary-positive-messages/

